verbose_text: Khakoo et al demonstrated that systemically injected MSCs reduced tumor growth in a model of Kaposi 's sarcoma through the inhibition of Akt, Zhu et al reported that human MSCs inhibited the proliferation of K562 cells by the secretion of Dickkopf related protein 1 (DKK-1).
evidence: inhibited the proliferation of K562 cells by the secretion of Dickkopf-related protein 1
